Short Description: Shibacals is a company that offers a range of physical goods integrated with NFC technology, providing additional benefits like VIP NFT access or surprise coupons.
Long Description: Shibacals aims to empower the crypto community by offering a diverse range of physical goods, from fashion items to toys and travel essentials. These products come with an NFC chip for added value, such as VIP NFT access or surprise coupons. The project is integrated with the Shibarium blockchain and focuses on delivering high-quality merchandise. They offer a seamless, end-to-end creation journey for their products, from 3D modeling to global distribution.
Target Audience: Crypto enthusiasts and the general public interested in physical goods with blockchain integration.

Short Description: ShibaPunkz is the first 10,000 NFT collection fully minted on Shibarium, featuring its own token, $SPUNK, as part of the 'Woofie Town' ecosystem. The project aims to build a strong community focused on crypto adoption and entertainment. It also integrates with $BONE for various features.
Long Description: ShibaPunkz is a pioneering NFT collection, being the first to fully mint 10,000 NFTs on the Shibarium blockchain. It features its own native token, $SPUNK, which is integral to its 'Woofie Town' ecosystem. After establishing its NFT collection as a potential original cornerstone of Shibarium, the $SPUNK token has gained increasing traction. The project has also launched the first lottery dapp on Shibarium, initially using $BONE and later incorporating $SPUNK. The token is slated to be the currency for future minting and will play a central role in upcoming Play-to-Earn (P2E) games, where the NFTs will be key characters. ShibaPunkz aims to build the strongest community in Shibarium, educating people on crypto adoption while providing entertainment. It seeks to continue the vision of Ryoshi by pushing for mass crypto adoption and contributing to the growth of the ShibArmy.
Target Audience: NFT enthusiasts and crypto lovers who enjoy building a community.

Short Description: Baby Brick Inu is a Shibarium-based 'Mutual Fund' offering a 3-token reward system. The project aims to become one of the most trusted on Shibarium, providing an instant diversified portfolio for holders. It also rewards with $BONE.
Long Description: Baby Brick Inu serves as a 'Mutual Fund' within the Shibarium ecosystem, offering a unique 3-token reward system. When investors buy one token, they effectively receive three tokens in total, diversifying their Shibarium portfolio instantly. The project's primary focus is to reward its holders 'Brick by Brick,' enabling them to earn $BONE tokens as well. Baby Brick Inu has locked 25% of its supply, which not only adds a layer of security but also acts as a token 'burn' mechanism. This locked wallet accrues both Brick by Brick Tokens and $BONE tokens, effectively reducing their overall supplies. The project aims to establish itself as one of the most trusted initiatives on Shibarium, offering both diversification and rewards to its community.

Short Description: $BRICK is a token fueling the 'Brick by Brick' initiative, aimed at promoting global Shibarium adoption. The DAO wallet, funded by a 3/3 tax and 1.5% $BONE rewards, supports various blockchain projects and innovations.
Long Description: Brick by Brick is a comprehensive initiative powered by the $BRICK token, with a limited supply of 100,000 and a 3/3 tax structure. It aims to accelerate global adoption of Shibarium, a blockchain platform. The initiative focuses on educating investors, supporting valuable blockchain projects, and investing in innovative technologies. A 1.5% $BONE reward is distributed to all BRICK holders, while another 1.5% goes into the DAO wallet for various use-cases like marketing and development. $BRICK holders can vote in the DAO and submit suggestions or project proposals, which are reviewed by Teh Foundation. Voting is conducted through the $BRICK DAO Dapp, and holders can 'sacrifice' their tokens for increased influence on critical decisions. The initiative offers affordable promotional opportunities and potential for direct DAO investments.

Short Description: WOOF Swap is a ve(3,3) Decentralized Exchange (DEX) built on Shibarium, focusing on liquidity and community-driven governance. It offers fast, cost-effective transactions and a robust incentivization model. Join the ShibArmy and earn rewards in $BONE.
Long Description: WOOF Swap is a community-driven DEX on the Shibarium network, offering a seamless blend of liquidity, voting, and rewards. It leverages zk-rollups and zero-knowledge proofs for efficient transactions. The protocol ensures a balanced distribution of rewards and emissions, encouraging strategic voting and early participation. Several measures have been implemented to promote productive gauges and ensure emissions are directed toward beneficial liquidity sources. WOOF Swap aims for a sustainable growth trajectory and long-term value for all stakeholders.

Short Description: WOOF Swap is a ve(3,3) DEX on Shibarium, focusing on liquidity and community governance. It offers fast transactions and incentivization. Earn rewards in $BONE with the ShibArmy.
Long Description: WOOF Swap is a community-led DEX on Shibarium, offering liquidity, voting, and rewards. Utilizing zk-rollups for efficiency, the protocol balances reward distribution and encourages strategic voting. Measures are in place to direct emissions to beneficial liquidity sources, aiming for sustainable growth and long-term value.

Short Description: Bark is a token that rewards and burns $SHIB for its holders.
Long Description: Bark offers its holders 2% $SHIB rewards and burns 1% $SHIB per transaction. The initial liquidity pool was burned, and half the supply was sent to Vitalik Buterin, following $SHIB's original strategy. Bark aims to strengthen both $SHIB and Shibarium communities through its rewards and is the first $SHIB reward and burn token on Shibarium.
Target Audience: Enthusiasts of $SHIB, Shiba Inu, and Shibarium, as well as those interested in earning $SHIB.

Short Description: Coinmerge (CMOS) is a multi-faceted Web3 enterprise offering a range of decentralized finance services and products.
Long Description: Based in Texas, USA, Coinmerge Technologies Inc. specializes in decentralized finance with over two years in the field. Their core product, the Coinmerge Operating System (CMOS), hosts a suite of decentralized apps for streamlined crypto trading and tracking. Beyond CMOS, Coinmerge serves as a marketing agency and offers a wide array of services like AMA sessions, KYC, and Smart Contract development. Targeting the Web3 ecosystem, they collaborate with Shibarium and Shiba-related projects. Their primary liquidity pair is $BONE.

Short Description: Sharbi, known as the 'Queen of Memes,' transcends the typical meme token stereotype. The project is on a mission for true decentralization, fostering a community that thrives on empowerment and aligns with the Shibarium ethos.
Long Description: Sharbi is a multifaceted crypto project on Shibarium. It offers educational resources through Shibarium University and financial tools like project whitelisting and staking rewards via its Solidity-based bridge. The DAO is evolving to provide passive income streams for holders. Sharbi actively engages its community through AMAs, partnerships, and initiatives like 'Artful Hearts' and 'Sharbi Gives Back.' It aims to be more than just a meme token, focusing on decentralization and empowerment.

ShortDescription: BabySPUNK is a captivating meme token on the Shibarium Blockchain. It offers its holders substantial rewards in Shibarium Punkz (SPUNK) for every transaction. The token imposes a 1% transaction limit and caps the maximum wallet size at 2%. Additionally, its liquidity is locked for a decade, ensuring long-term stability.
LongDescription: BabySPUNK is not just another meme token; it's a burgeoning community on the Shibarium Blockchain. With a limited total supply of 1,000,000 tokens, it aims to be a valuable asset for its holders. Both buying and selling transactions incur a 5% fee, which is distributed as 1% burn and 4% rewards to holders. The project is committed to long-term sustainability, continually expanding its team with specialists. BabySPUNK is more than a token; it's a movement aiming to spread humor, entertainment, and a sense of community among its holders.

Short Description: Marswap Farming Token ($MSWAPF) is the governance token of the number one Marswap Exchange on Shibarium.
Long Description: Marswap Farming Token ($MSWAPF) redefines DeFi on the Shibarium Chain by incentivizing liquidity providers and stakers through its innovative rewards system. $MSWAPF empowers users to participate actively, generating rewards while contributing to the Marswap ecosystem's growth.

Short Description: ChewySwap is the leading Community-Based decentralized exchange on Shibarium and Dogechain, the two leading EVM compatible blockchains for Dog lovers.
Long Description: ChewySwap is a unique decentralized exchange (DEX) operating on Shibarium and Dogechain, designed to optimize your Doggy Blockchain trading experience. The platform offers a range of features including NFTs, Staking, and Farming. ChewySwap is committed to transparency and security, with audited smart contracts and an experienced development team. It also pledges 2% of all trading fees to animal charities, as voted on by the community. The platform offers low, near-zero fees and various ways to earn tokens, making it a comprehensive solution for both seasoned DeFi traders and newcomers.
Target Audience: DeFi traders, Liquidity Providers, SHIB holders, Crypto Newbies

Company Name: The Shiba Sequoia Forest Lads NFT Collection
Short Description: A unique 10,000-piece music NFT collection featuring 25 songs from web3 musicians, 3D artwork, and tangible benefits including annual festival tickets, music publishing rights, and artwork IP rights.
Long Description: The Shiba Sequoia Forest Lads NFT Collection comprises 10,000 unique NFTs, each featuring a song from web3 musicians, 3D artwork created by the project initiator, and a myriad of benefits. Holders of these NFTs gain annual access to all ShibaFest festivals, publishing rights to the music, and intellectual property rights to the artwork. In a unique twist, each NFT also includes a claim for a Giant Sequoia Tree clone, originating from a tree planted by the musicians at the festivals. The project is establishing nurseries, festivals, and other businesses to provide rewards to NFT holders, liquidity for the DAO, and support for the entire ecosystem. Through art, music, blockchain technology, and tree preservation, this collection and DAO aim to enrich both local and web3 communities, adding value to local economies and the Shibarium platform.
